  - Description: Validated knowledge in network security, risk management, and incident response.

- **Certified Ethical Hacker (CEH) – EC-Council**  
  - Date of Completion: [Insert Date]  
  - Description: Gained hands-on experience in ethical hacking techniques and penetration testing methodologies.

*(If you have completed any other certifications, please list them here with the date and brief description.)*

